{"tid":515051,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"「尋人」","createTime":"2017-12-31T06:02:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-02T14:33:32.000Z","uid":108956,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"433ccc2584aea3c74c0bd0d7d1cfc35cad7c07ce","tid":515051,"uid":108956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T06:02:30.000Z","msg":"「尋人」元朗<br />\n12月28日<br />\n 希望搵返個黑框眼鏡 男仔 。元朗千色買精品嗰度。我已經見到你哋望住我朋友。<br />\n   去到麵包爸爸嗰邊，咁啱又見到你哋。黑框眼鏡個男仔行去我朋友身邊，似想問佢拎電話。但又唔敢。而我哋趕住買嘢飲就走左。<br />\n    <br />\n而個男仔特徵係 黑框眼鏡 運動型 身高應該172或以上 。而個男仔同行嘅有 戴冷㡌嘅男仔同一個女仔。<br />\n <br />\n    如果有緣嘅話，你睇到呢個post。希望可以搵到你。<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nPs:代fd po"},{"pid":"b4dab589dcb1ec59b9b95ac52c11d3e7e2297ee7","tid":515051,"uid":162980,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T06:17:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0870d6a390bf1d42bd2936ec82291859ee39e320","tid":515051,"uid":59961,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T06:18:49.000Z","msg":"死開d啦5p😌"},{"pid":"f806e1740f3cc51c5aa627312f8ddc96778000d2","tid":515051,"uid":28163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4dab589dcb1ec59b9b95ac52c11d3e7e2297ee7","tid":515051,"uid":162980,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T06:17:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T06:20:13.000Z","msg":"係 所以樓主死心"},{"pid":"4f741d4da0b594bef65783b58e391f8f34b28c36","tid":515051,"uid":863,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T06:20:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"96eb37f3d104f911d407931fb1abf670a19b8ee0","tid":515051,"uid":140802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T06:22:49.000Z","msg":"格劍<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6db6e4bb756629310c5576276a2626f442b2025","tid":515051,"uid":108956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T06:44:16.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile